---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StickyFooter from '../components/StickyFooter.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | DealsHub India">
  <main class="prose reveal">
    <h1 class="text-5xl mb-12">About Us</h1>
    <p class="font-bold text-xl mb-8">Back in 2018, DealsHub was initially started from a WhatsApp group as a team of dedicated bargain hunters.</p>
    <p>We are a team that scours the internet to bring you the best deals and discounts on a wide range of products—from fashion and beauty to home and garden, we cover it all. Our goal is simple: to help you save money on the things you love. We do the legwork, so you don’t have to.</p>
    <p>We search high and low for discounts, coupons, and promotions, and compile them all in one convenient place for you. We are constantly updating our website with the latest deals and offers, so be sure to check back often. Thank you for visiting DealsHub. Happy shopping!</p>
    
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
      <a href="/" class="text-whatsapp-green font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase no-underline hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">&larr; Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <StickyFooter />
</Layout>
